asset.name: Harborfront Residences
asset.description: A luxury residential and commercial complex located along the waterfront. Features high-end apartments, retail spaces, direct marina access, and a vibrant boardwalk with restaurants and entertainment venues. Designed as a prime lifestyle destination integrating leisure and living in one hub.
asset.staking: Stakers earn a percentage of rental yield from long-term leases, short-term vacation rentals, and retail tenancy agreements. Additional staking rewards come from seasonal tourism surges and event-based premium pricing.
